_sText:
ba_ jail _jurassic _park_ v2

A complet rework from my old "ba_jurassic_park_v1", everything is changed and now is better :).

- Fixed lag on round start.
- Fixed some buttons not triggering on damage.
- Removed disco area.
- Removed raptor area.
- Added dodgeball minigame.
- Added roullete and mini roullete colors minigame.
- Added a new colours game.
- Reworked soccer game.
- Reworked everything related to the environment and ambience sounds.
- Reworked death race.
- Reworked tt's jail and armory.
- Reworked Rope Game
- Added some easter eggs
- Added mini map radar.
